2015年9月9日，隨著[[iPhone_6S|iPhone 6S]]和iPhone 6S Plus的發布，iPhone 6及iPhone 6 Plus被移至iPhone系列裡的中端產品行列。iPhone 6及iPhone 6 Plus的128GB版本以及兩款手機的金色版本經已停售，然而iPhone 6及iPhone 6 Plus的16GB和64GB版本銀色和太空灰仍以低價出售<ref>{{cite news | url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/15/09/09/apple-axes-gold-color-128gb-options-for-iphone-6-and-6-plus-models | title=Apple axes gold color, 128 GB options for iPhone 6 and 6 Plus models | work=Apple Insider | date=2015-09-09 | accessdate=2016-01-10 | author=Campbell, Mikey | archive-date=2016-01-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109160710/http://appleinsider.com/articles/15/09/09/apple-axes-gold-color-128gb-options-for-iphone-6-and-6-plus-models | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年6月，蘋果公司在中國面臨潛在的銷售禁令，作為中國設備製造商的深圳百利，據稱iPhone 6和iPhone 6 Plus侵犯了其外觀設計專利<ref>Abhishek, [http://www.techkabaap.com/patent-fight-stop-apple-iphone-6-sales-china/ "Patent Fight Could Stop Apple iPhone 6 Sales in China] {{Wayback|url=http://www.techkabaap.com/patent-fight-stop-apple-iphone-6-sales-china/ |date=20170807120357 }}, Techkabaap, August 3, 2017. Retrieved August 3, 2017.</ref>。

