== 規格 ==
=== 硬件 ===
iPhone 6和iPhone 6 Plus的設計受到[[iPad_Air|iPad Air]]的影響，其有著顯示器彎曲邊緣的玻璃面板，而背後的鋁質包含著兩根天線的塑料條<ref name=verge-6review>{{cite news|title=iPhone 6 review|url=https://www.theverge.com/2014/9/16/6154975/iphone-6-review|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|first=David|last=Pierce|date=2014-09-16|accessdate=2014-09-23|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826074619/https://www.theverge.com/2014/9/16/6154975/iphone-6-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。背面是由6000系列的鋁質製成<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.wired.com/2015/09/iphone-6s-6s-plus-biggest-changes-invisible/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2019-08-26 |archive-date=2018-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116111853/https://www.wired.com/2015/09/iphone-6s-6s-plus-biggest-changes-invisible/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。所有型號均採用金色，銀色和「太空灰」的飾面。iPhone 6的厚度為{{convert | 6.9 | mm}}，而iPhone 6 Plus的厚度為{{convert | 7.1 | mm | abbr = on}}；兩者都比[[iPhone_5C|iPhone 5C]]和[[iPhone_5S|iPhone 5S]]更薄，使iPhone 6成為迄今為止蘋果公司最薄的手機。iPhone 6及iPhone 6 Plus最重要的變化就是其顯示器，兩者都被稱為「[[Retina顯示器|Retina顯示器]]」和「強化離子」，iPhone 6顯示屏的尺寸為4.7英寸，以{{le|16：9縱橫比|16:9 aspect ratio}}的1334x750分辨率（326{{le|ppi|Pixels per inch}}減去一行像素）；而iPhone 6 Plus顯示屏的尺寸為5.5英寸，其分辨率為1920x1080（401ppi）。其顯示器採用多域液晶顯示面板，稱為「雙域像素」；RGB像素本身在圖案中傾斜，因此可以從不同的角度中看到每個像素。該項技術有助於改善顯示器的視角<ref name=anandtech-dualdomain>{{cite web|title=Understanding Dual-Domain Pixels in the iPhone 6 and 6 Plus|url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/8509/understanding-dual-domain-pixels-in-the-iphone-6-and-iphone-6-plus|website=Anandtech|publisher=Purch Inc.|accessdate=2015-03-01|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826074624/https://www.anandtech.com/show/8509/understanding-dual-domain-pixels-in-the-iphone-6-and-iphone-6-plus|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

為了適應更大尺寸的iPhone 6和iPhone 6 Plus，電源按鈕的位置從頂部移至手機的側面以提高其輔助功能<ref name=verge-announce /><ref name=verge-sixplusannounce />。iPhone 6配備了6.91 Wh （1,810 mAh）電池，而iPhone 6 Plus配備了11.1 Wh（2,915 mAh）電池。它與之前的型號有所不同，其後置攝像頭並非跟裝置的後方完全齊平，而是略微突出<ref name=verge-bulge>{{cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/2014/9/16/6209759/apple-has-an-embarassing-bulge|title=Apple is hiding an embarrassing iPhone 6 camera bulge|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|first=Tom|last=Warren|date=2014-09-16|accessdate=2014-09-16|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826074619/https://www.theverge.com/2014/9/16/6209759/apple-has-an-embarassing-bulge|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

兩款機型都包括[[Apple_A8|Apple A8]][[系統單晶片|系統單晶片]]，及{{le|M8動態處理器|Apple motion coprocessors}}—那是[[iPhone_5S|iPhone 5S]] {{le|M7動態處理器|Apple motion coprocessors}}的更新版，原先的M7動態處理器與現時所用M8動態處理器之間的主要區別，還包括測量海拔高度變化的氣壓計。{{le|菲爾·席勒|Phil Schiller}}吹捧指與5s相比，A8芯片會提高25％的CPU性能，提升50％的圖形處理性能，並減少熱量輸出。早期提交的報告顯示，A8的GPU性能可能確實在每年的發布中以翻倍的性能脫離前幾代產品，在對比5s，5和4s中，其獲得分數分別為21204.26（iPhone6S）、20253.80（iPhone5S）、10973.6（iPhone5）及5034.75（iPhone4S）<ref name=gsmarena-benchmark>{{cite web|url=http://www.gsmarena.com/iphone_6_a8_gpu_benchmark_suggests_its_behind_the_curve-news-9630.php|title=iPhone 6 A8 GPU benchmark suggests it's behind the curve|work=GSMArena|date=2014-09-12|accessdate=2014-09-16|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826074641/https://www.gsmarena.com/iphone_6_a8_gpu_benchmark_suggests_its_behind_the_curve-news-9630.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在iPhone 6和iPhone 6 Plus上擴展的[[長期演進技術|長期演進技術（LTE）]]連接為已改良的[[進階長期演進技術|進階長期演進技術（LTE-A）]]，支援超過20個LTE頻段（比iPhone 5s多7個）<ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=https://www.apple.com/iphone-6/specs/|title=Apple – iPhone 6 – Connectivity|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple]]|date=2014-09-09|accessdate=2014-09-10|archive-date=2016-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160406153541/https://www.apple.com/iphone-6/specs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，高達150M bit/s的下載速度，以及支援[[長期演進語音承載|長期演進VoiceOver]]。[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]性能也得到改善至支援[[IEEE_802.11ac|IEEE 802.11ac]]的規範，提供高達433.0581M bit/s的速度，比[[IEEE_802.11n|IEEE 802.11n]]快３倍<ref name=":0" />，以及支援可用的{{le|Wi-Fi撥打|Generic Access Network}}功能。iPhone 6及iPhone 6 Plus還支援[[近場通訊|近距離無線通訊]]（NFC）。它最初專門用於[[Apple_Pay|Apple Pay]]—一個新的[[流動支付|流動支付]]系統，允許用戶把他們的信用卡儲存於[[Apple_Wallet|Apple銀包]]中，用於通過NFC進行在線支付和零售購物<ref name=cnet-applepay>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnet.com/news/apple-adds-nfc-to-iphone-6-with-apple-pay|title=Apple takes NFC mainstream on iPhone 6; Apple Watch with Apple Pay|work=[[CNET|CNET]]|first1=Marguerite|last1=Reardon|first2=Shara|last2=Tibken|date=2014-09-09|accessdate=2014-09-10|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826080138/https://www.cnet.com/news/apple-adds-nfc-to-iphone-6-with-apple-pay/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=cultofmac-applepaynfc>{{cite web|url=http://www.cultofmac.com/296093/apple-confirms-iphone-6-nfc-apple-pay|title=Apple confirms iPhone 6 NFC chip is only for Apple Pay at launch|first=Buster|last=Hein|date=2014-09-15|accessdate=2014-09-15|archive-date=2019-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826074640/https://www.cultofmac.com/296093/apple-confirms-iphone-6-nfc-apple-pay/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了Apple Pay之外，[[iOS_11|iOS 11]]還為第三方應用程式新增了近場通信的有限度使用權<ref name="engadget-nfcios11">{{cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2018/05/25/apple-will-reportedly-open-up-nfc-in-ios-12/|title=iOS 12 will reportedly include new NFC features, enable iPhones to become secure hotel room keys|last=|first=|date=|website=9to5mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190826074619/https://9to5mac.com/2018/05/25/apple-will-reportedly-open-up-nfc-in-ios-12/|archive-date=2019-08-26|dead-url=no|accessdate=2019-04-29}}</ref>。

iPhone 6的後置鏡頭現在能夠以30fps或60fps的速度拍攝1080p的視頻，和以120fps或240fps的速度拍攝720p慢動作視頻，亦可以製作3至10秒的縮時錄影。相機還包括[[自動對焦|自動對焦]]功能<ref name=engadget-review>{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2014/09/16/iphone-6-and-6-plus-review|title=iPhone 6 and 6 Plus review: bigger and better, but with stiffer competition|publisher=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|date=2014-09-16|accessdate=2014-09-24|archive-date=2019-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721081737/http://www.engadget.com/2014/09/16/iphone-6-and-6-plus-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，iPhone 6 Plus的相機規格是幾乎完全相同的，但當中加入了[[影像穩定器|光學防震]]<ref name=verge-announce /><ref name=verge-sixplusannounce />。前置攝像頭還更新了新傳感器和f/2.2光圈，以及支援[[連拍|連拍]]及[[高動態範圍成像|HDR模式]]<ref name=verge-announce /><ref name=verge-sixplusannounce />。

